{"tid":2339211,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"【求救】聖誕禮物殺人事件","createTime":"2020-12-24T13:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T13:41:23.000Z","uid":31827,"like":113,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"23a73263220a41c5472136a912b940fc6bbdf8c1","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:00:13.000Z","msg":"是咁的，琴晚係同事屋企聚餐，飲大兩杯，講到交換聖誕禮物既時候，女同事Rebecca抽到我個no.。理論上佢要比禮物我，但係佢冇準備，於是佢口快快咁話送自己比我。<br />\n<br />\n我以為佢講笑，誰不知&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"green\"><span class=\"x-large\">叮噹──！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我急不及待去開門，心裡卜通卜通地跳。打開了門，一份巨大的禮物箱放在門口。奇怪的是，送貨的人沒有要我簽名就走了，為什麼他這麼肯定我家中有人呢？<br />\n<br />\n這個重量&hellip;&hellip;剛好可以裝起一個人。我想像Rebecca就坐在裡面的樣子，待會打開之後，我要好好一層層地拆開這份禮物。<br />\n<br />\n我小心翼翼地推著禮物入門口。嗯──？這個重量&hellip;&hellip;不太對勁，Rebecca應該沒有那麼輕吧？<br />\n<br />\n我輕輕打開箱子的包裝，裡面仍是一個包裝。我再打開。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>頭髮&hellip;&hellip;？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我摸到頭髮了。一下子，緊張的心情再次衝擊我的大腦，Rebecca果然是說真的。我輕輕撫摸她的頭髮，這&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n嗯？<br />\n<br />\n濕濕的。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>血！？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n從剛才開始，我就聞到一股臭味。打開箱子之後，便更加明顯了。我狐疑，心裡有一股不舒服的感覺。輕輕拍了拍Rebecca的頭。<br />\n<br />\n「喂&hellip;&hellip;咩事&hellip;&hellip;？」話剛出口，Rebecca的頭一個滾&hellip;&hellip;滾到地上。<br />\n<br />\n在頭之下，只有一座石塊。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">啊──！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">救命，救命！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n這不是發夢吧？Rebecca&hellip;&hellip;死了？<br />\n<br />\nRebecca臉無血色，前一刻我還在猜想這是不是她的惡作劇，當我摸到她的皮膚之後，幾乎可以肯定我遇上了可怕的事情。<br />\n<br />\n我甚至來不及反應。<br />\n<br />\n要&hellip;&hellip;要報警嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己命案自己破<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵警犬幫手"},{"pid":"ebee2f3a4fc5709ce9e9db2dfea33a8425ba9fb5","tid":2339211,"uid":167260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:01:16.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b441651f6a6d2cf068ca5bd9134ff8b5abba1a91","tid":2339211,"uid":136700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:01:40.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c940931b92388693d69ccdb9455aada42ab7ed88","tid":2339211,"uid":300690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:01:49.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0370fdd90613a3be27f583700463a238116ad028","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ebee2f3a4fc5709ce9e9db2dfea33a8425ba9fb5","tid":2339211,"uid":167260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:01:16.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:01:57.000Z","msg":"冇出街咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50d9cb2659f13d861ef7fff0a6fd133de836d24","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:02:16.000Z","msg":"主席要求點人數<br />\n平安夜真毒撚"},{"pid":"fe70bec8200d8e2cf7845c6f7d3b268be1d80d9a","tid":2339211,"uid":167260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0370fdd90613a3be27f583700463a238116ad028","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ebee2f3a4fc5709ce9e9db2dfea33a8425ba9fb5","tid":2339211,"uid":167260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:01:16.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:01:57.000Z","msg":"冇出街咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:02:29.000Z","msg":"都要入嚟推咗正經嘢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84e06ba942c9930ea1f28e2f824ccb2a82d7ba79","tid":2339211,"uid":48080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:03:07.000Z","msg":"呃正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dfaebb5be8aedc99bedeb3dcef663629759b9f0","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"84e06ba942c9930ea1f28e2f824ccb2a82d7ba79","tid":2339211,"uid":48080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:03:07.000Z","msg":"呃正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死唔斷氣既你"},{"pid":"cfd241a31d37db76c9e8b7863076d5f7a7046bbd","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fe70bec8200d8e2cf7845c6f7d3b268be1d80d9a","tid":2339211,"uid":167260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0370fdd90613a3be27f583700463a238116ad028","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ebee2f3a4fc5709ce9e9db2dfea33a8425ba9fb5","tid":2339211,"uid":167260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:01:16.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:01:57.000Z","msg":"冇出街咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:02:29.000Z","msg":"都要入嚟推咗正經嘢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:04:36.000Z","msg":"記得戴"},{"pid":"3ebd47bebe57178e43163acd6d4ea6226c6c9fb4","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c940931b92388693d69ccdb9455aada42ab7ed88","tid":2339211,"uid":300690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:01:49.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:04:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好快手"},{"pid":"7a1b9aa652f50bd1798ac6624a9f1557578457a2","tid":2339211,"uid":167260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dfaebb5be8aedc99bedeb3dcef663629759b9f0","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"84e06ba942c9930ea1f28e2f824ccb2a82d7ba79","tid":2339211,"uid":48080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:03:07.000Z","msg":"呃正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死唔斷氣既你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:05:18.000Z","msg":"比咗負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60efebb38be213e8a94c0a2c47d4e6b938a3de2","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7a1b9aa652f50bd1798ac6624a9f1557578457a2","tid":2339211,"uid":167260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dfaebb5be8aedc99bedeb3dcef663629759b9f0","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"84e06ba942c9930ea1f28e2f824ccb2a82d7ba79","tid":2339211,"uid":48080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:03:07.000Z","msg":"呃正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死唔斷氣既你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:05:18.000Z","msg":"比咗負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:06:16.000Z","msg":"屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲諗緊邊個咁快手負皮"},{"pid":"38e7158f9d7c48612949e7331ac276ff1f7aeaa4","tid":2339211,"uid":167260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e60efebb38be213e8a94c0a2c47d4e6b938a3de2","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7a1b9aa652f50bd1798ac6624a9f1557578457a2","tid":2339211,"uid":167260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dfaebb5be8aedc99bedeb3dcef663629759b9f0","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死唔斷氣既你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:05:18.000Z","msg":"比咗負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:06:16.000Z","msg":"屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲諗緊邊個咁快手負皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:06:39.000Z","msg":"想睇你點作落去嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a7d6a0bc61ea958d20cf9e6c053f67aa4c1cef","tid":2339211,"uid":93199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:06:44.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"a3821053c5298a9176fe8b7542c2b85d23a708ba","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:07:30.000Z","msg":"理性告訴我應該報警，但直覺卻在告訴我，報警只會對我更不利。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">「嘻嘻──」</span></span>這個時候，我突然聽到門外傳來笑聲。我定睛一看，發現自己剛才太過興奮，並沒有關門。<br />\n<br />\n是誰在偷看？<br />\n<br />\n是誰在偷笑？<br />\n<br />\n我馬上衝了出去！四下無人，我追上去幾步。那個人卻像是憑空消失了似的，再也找不到了。<br />\n<br />\n我折返回家，這時候，更糟糕的事情發生了──<br />\n<br />\n門被關上了。<br />\n<br />\n我&hellip;&hellip;什麼都沒有帶走。<br />\n<br />\n要跟保安說明嗎？要找開鎖佬門？<br />\n<br />\n不，要是他們幫忙開門的話，一推門口便會看到Rebecca的頭就在地上。那時候，我將會成為真正的殺人兇手。<br />\n<br />\nRebecca為什麼死了？兇手又為什麼要把她的頭部寄給我？<br />\n<br />\n我太緊張，太無助，什麼都思考不了。我身上只有一套衣服，沒有電話，沒有銀包，一時之間不知道可以怎樣做。<br />\n<br />\n在大快活坐了一會兒之後，我開始冷靜下來。不管這是發生了什麼事，我也應該冷靜地處理。這已經可以肯定不是惡作劇，而是真實的殺人事件。<br />\n<br />\n昨天晚上到底發生了什麼事？我們散場後，Rebecca遇上了什麼？<br />\n<br />\n平靜下來，我發現自己一個電話號碼都記不起，然而我卻記得肥仔波的家在哪裡。<br />\n<br />\n──因為昨晚我們就是到肥仔波的家中慶祝。我硬著頭皮向路人借了交通費，來到肥仔波的家中。<br />\n<br />\n門鈴按了好幾下，沒有人答應。我按了快五分鐘，正當我打算失望離開的時候，門開了。<br />\n<br />\n「呀波，好彩你係屋企。」可能是昨晚飲大了，肥仔波睡死了。<br />\n<br />\n他的神情有點緊張，問：「咦，點解你會黎左既？」"},{"pid":"aa109384b03c3ce9a924b187b7e6e725d4e4bf03","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:07:46.000Z","msg":"「我&hellip;&hellip;」我不知道如何解釋，但這件事不適宜告訴其他人，所以我隨便找了個藉口糊混過去：「我屋企熱水爐壞左呀，搵左人上去整，呢2日冇地方沖涼，唔知你呢到方唔方便呢？」<br />\n<br />\n肥仔波想了一想，臉有難色。雖然在公司中我和他的交情最好，然而這樣的請求的確是強人所難，這一點我也是明白的。<br />\n<br />\n「可&hellip;&hellip;可以係可以&hellip;&hellip;不過&hellip;&hellip;你&hellip;&hellip;你可唔可以等我一陣？」肥仔波說自己的家在昨晚狂歡之後沒有收拾好，所以要我在門口等他一會兒，他先清潔一下。<br />\n<br />\n「入黎啦。」<br />\n<br />\n終於找了個地方安頓下來。但是長久下去也不是辦法，一旦Rebecca的頭在我家中放久了，就會發出惡臭，也會被鄰居發現的。<br />\n<br />\n當務之急，我必須想辦法。<br />\n<br />\n「做咩你個樣，咁驚青？做左虧心事呀？」<br />\n<br />\n「下？」經肥仔波一提醒，我才知道自己已經喜怒形於色。這樣的話，就算我沒有做過，別人也認為我是罪犯。<br />\n<br />\n接下來我應該怎辦？<br />\n<br />\n接下來我應該怎辦？<br />\n<br />\n接下來我應該怎辦？<br />\n<br />\n「你有咩諗唔通呀？同我分享一下啦，或者我可以幫到你。」肥仔波對我說。真是的&hellip;&hellip;突然之間，他變成了我唯一能夠信任的人。<br />\n<br />\n然而我應該思考的，卻是Rebecca的去向。我整理了一下事情的來龍去脈。"},{"pid":"213f35b12bfe2d2565005e4e531ce8ddc27c7926","tid":2339211,"uid":10484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:18:51.000Z","msg":"銀妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd951675b794761094b015802aa431a7787de92","tid":2339211,"uid":247639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0370fdd90613a3be27f583700463a238116ad028","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ebee2f3a4fc5709ce9e9db2dfea33a8425ba9fb5","tid":2339211,"uid":167260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:01:16.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:01:57.000Z","msg":"冇出街咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:20:23.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"9199c85f0da7beb89344eec4a5a33b406e2cf37d","tid":2339211,"uid":247639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"213f35b12bfe2d2565005e4e531ce8ddc27c7926","tid":2339211,"uid":10484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:18:51.000Z","msg":"銀妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b6c9a3e7bf02066074e93082b2108be93b4ff9","tid":2339211,"uid":35946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:30:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4424dcf5901d32facfc9e2b690623dde55d7ae","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"213f35b12bfe2d2565005e4e531ce8ddc27c7926","tid":2339211,"uid":10484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:18:51.000Z","msg":"銀妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b488552da989da5e63d19046a7b825cd912ec591","tid":2339211,"uid":136918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:05:58.000Z","msg":"LM!!!!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"0c422c176825ccf342c7fa9397f7261f52f40560","tid":2339211,"uid":386772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:09:44.000Z","msg":"長/短故?"},{"pid":"4ded68f3ad3e2fd978835699b55e80e59435cb42","tid":2339211,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:10:19.000Z","msg":"阿銀～"},{"pid":"90ab6af6ace136b94a806fde0239b6827368fd38","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c422c176825ccf342c7fa9397f7261f52f40560","tid":2339211,"uid":386772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:09:44.000Z","msg":"長/短故?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:50:29.000Z","msg":"短短地"},{"pid":"e705f56c7151e8f6d83a8de788fe63529635fd92","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4ded68f3ad3e2fd978835699b55e80e59435cb42","tid":2339211,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:10:19.000Z","msg":"阿銀～"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:50:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />hey"},{"pid":"61388cf9966c9706a0bc44063f86ef9ba28681a6","tid":2339211,"uid":305287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:54:14.000Z","msg":"新po lm"},{"pid":"3a116af497582fde8d82d5d81ea81632b5b9ad1c","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"61388cf9966c9706a0bc44063f86ef9ba28681a6","tid":2339211,"uid":305287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:54:14.000Z","msg":"新po lm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:14:57.000Z","msg":"咁撚正個故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等你地扑完嘢返嚟睇"},{"pid":"dc1afab892ab589a085ca8266b0c7056011c127f","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T16:03:58.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9de23c5bf73286d67df3f9671c1f1460cd37d6ce","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T16:04:14.000Z","msg":"在兩個星期之前，公司的女同事Maggie提議我們放聖誕節假前最後一聚，當時響應這個活動的有Maggie、Rebecca、我、男同事呀龍和肥仔波五人，原本department head Eric 都來，不過他臨時有事，所以前一天通知我們參加不了。<br />\n<br />\n當天公司2點收工，我們買齊東西後就到了肥仔波的家中，那時候大概已經四時多吧。玩了一會兒switch之後，我們開始飲酒和打邊爐。這個過程中並沒有任何異常。硬要說的話，就是Maggie人曾經落過7仔買酒，那時候客廳只有我和Rebecca兩個人，然而我們並沒有什麼交雜，我也沒有察覺得到Rebecca有什麼異樣。<br />\n<br />\n就這樣持續到9點多，在飲了不少酒之後，我們開始交換禮物。由於eric的退出，Rebecca的送禮對象變成了我，但她似乎沒有準備禮物，所以開玩笑式地說將自己作為禮物送給我。<br />\n<br />\nRebecca還透露自己沒有男朋友，剛好我也沒有女朋友，或者可以試一試。我們都知道那是開玩笑的，我沒有想過Rebecca真的「送」了一份「禮物」給我，而且還是這麼一大份。<br />\n<br />\n11點多，我們陸續收拾東西離開，我們四個人原本打算坐的士離開，但是Rebecca表示自己有下場，要出尖沙咀。她看起來沒有很醉，所以我們就任她自己離開了。<br />\n<br />\n直到那個時候，並沒有任何異樣。<br />\n<br />\n問題是在11點離後了肥仔波的家中之後，發生了什麼事？在我們分開以後，Rebecca難道遇人不淑，因而被殺害了嗎？但是兇手卻偏偏把Rebecca的頭部包成禮物送給我，這可能是一種巧合。<br />\n<br />\n然而我的心中卻有一種可怕的直覺油然而生──<br />\n<br />\n這&hellip;&hellip;或者是我們其中一個人做的。<br />\n<br />\nMaggie。<br />\n<br />\n呀龍。<br />\n<br />\n肥仔波。"},{"pid":"e0bb4f4ff54117ef1ea65fbba0b1509ff9ec8253","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T18:44:21.000Z","msg":"自己推"},{"pid":"5dacdb81f452d8f16bb9e4bfd7eca44d297cb314","tid":2339211,"uid":10484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T19:26:57.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54939bb63a706a5d9c5e37aef34a3d5eb2202d5f","tid":2339211,"uid":10484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T19:28:03.000Z","msg":"諗起聖誕禮物係要幫人洗廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c31f778fd4c304284b025ec7f7c48c589024200","tid":2339211,"uid":30601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T19:46:52.000Z","msg":"似係肥仔波做嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab077d6107b5c241ae60202679c4d0cb5d5d82e","tid":2339211,"uid":313162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T19:55:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616cbc1180d42401958a429e54c8596f40fb647d","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8c31f778fd4c304284b025ec7f7c48c589024200","tid":2339211,"uid":30601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T19:46:52.000Z","msg":"似係肥仔波做嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07bb193299d70afd28eb603269f9828d0108005b","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"54939bb63a706a5d9c5e37aef34a3d5eb2202d5f","tid":2339211,"uid":10484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T19:28:03.000Z","msg":"諗起聖誕禮物係要幫人洗廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:02:33.000Z","msg":"熟口熟面好似聽過"},{"pid":"b24798b7b37f8ada7e0e187fb146d14608e85cad","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:12:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"174c28f85460c69df1d22b2747fb2c47e74372f8","tid":2339211,"uid":386772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:15:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a853cee651c0d380facd824dc48d44335dd5a698","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:27:54.000Z","msg":"我看了一眼肥仔波。<br />\n<br />\n當我萌生了這種想法之後，居然對他產生懷疑了：為什麼他沒有馬上開門，為什麼他看起來如此緊張？<br />\n<br />\n那麼，我在他的家中會否有危險？<br />\n<br />\n一個肢解屍體的兇手，沒有什麼做不出來。<br />\n<br />\n「你頭先真係嚇死我，係咁按門鐘。」沒等我懷疑，肥仔波自己說了原因：「唔知係咪琴晚食太多，哈哈，我今朝一起身就係咁柯，驚臭親你。」<br />\n<br />\n「哦──」我恍然大悟。看來是我多疑了，看得太多金田一，害我都懷疑起身邊的人來。<br />\n<br />\n「係呢&hellip;&hellip;」我試探肥仔波的反應：「你琴晚之後有冇同Rebecca聯絡？」<br />\n<br />\n肥仔波表情沒有任何變化，似乎不知道這件事。反問我：「下？我冇啦啦做咩搵佢？你搵佢有野咩？」<br />\n<br />\n「冇&hellip;&hellip;呀，我仲未收到佢份禮物呀嘛。」"},{"pid":"15721db14839537026b7fc5210a29e118ba60b7b","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:28:37.000Z","msg":"肥仔波皺眉頭思考我的話，露出如夢初醒的樣子：「下，你以為佢真係會獻身比你？30歲人唔好ff咁多啦。」<br />\n<br />\n哈&hellip;&hellip;哈哈&hellip;&hellip;我陪笑。最起碼&hellip;&hellip;知道這個地方、這個人是安全的。<br />\n<br />\n「係喇，你係技術支援嫁嘛&hellip;&hellip;」我問肥仔波：「有冇可能&hellip;&hellip;其實你識得開鎖呢？」<br />\n<br />\n「開鎖就搵開鎖佬啦。」肥仔波不置可否。但是以我對他的了解，他是很喜歡魔術和一些小把戲的人，也許&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n「實不相瞞，我最近想學d魔術。」聽到「魔術」兩個字，肥仔波雙眼發光了，追著問：「你最近有機會用到？」<br />\n<br />\n我思疑了一下，點點頭，肥仔波更加興奮地問我：「係關於咩既？物體消失？」他把話題拉得更遠了，我打斷了他的話，說：「我見youtube d人開鎖好型，但係我就係唔明。唔知&hellip;&hellip;你會唔會識呢？」"},{"pid":"f2214091b65cb70b0de735e626c5693dcd7f925a","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:28:55.000Z","msg":"肥仔波露出了失望的神情，徐徐地說道：「開鎖&hellip;&hellip;應該唔係魔術黎，係好簡單既原理。」<br />\n<br />\n這次興奮的人變成我了：「你可唔可以教我？」<br />\n<br />\n「下？」<br />\n<br />\n「嗯？」<br />\n<br />\n「你唔係諗住&hellip;&hellip;？你大好前途喎。」<br />\n<br />\n我不想把自己的難處告訴他，只好不斷編理由。幸好肥仔波最後相信了我的話，沒有多問。他只教了我兩三小時，我能夠掌握得到技巧。幸好我家的門鎖並不複雜，在普通五金鋪買的，一般的技能便開得了。<br />\n<br />\n我向肥仔波借了些工具，假裝自己在進行維修，成功開了家門。<br />\n<br />\n終於&hellip;&hellip;回來了。<br />\n<br />\nXxxxxxx"},{"pid":"57bca702184e628a197a279602a42e2fd39345c2","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:29:54.000Z","msg":"嗯？<br />\n<br />\n這裡是我的家嗎？我遲疑了一會兒，然而這裡的一切都如平常一樣，沒有半點變化。<br />\n<br />\n沒有變化，正是這一切最奇怪的地方。<br />\n<br />\nRebecca的頭，就在正中央的頭&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我取回自己的手機和銀包，用133打電話給Rebecca，有人接！<br />\n<br />\n「喂？」<br />\n<br />\n「喂，Rebecca？」我在電話的另一邊呼喚了將近兩分鐘，卻沒有回覆。如果不是Rebecca的話，那&hellip;&hellip;是誰接聽了電話？<br />\n<br />\n兇手！<br />\n<br />\n我連忙掛線。兇手&hellip;&hellip;鎖定了我？<br />\n<br />\nRebecca死了。"},{"pid":"e83d2d2c10f3ae9b81c1ecb451979ad0fd408f99","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:31:56.000Z","msg":"血差不多乾了，我清洗了很多遍，仍無法洗淨血漬。在這個時刻，我做了一個連自己也不敢相信的行動：我冷靜地包好Rebecca的頭，將雪櫃裡的東西統統拿了來，把Rebecca的頭放進冰格中。我有種直覺，屍體總會給我一些提示，只是現在的我還未想通。<br />\n<br />\n要是對方存心陷害我的話，絕不會那麼簡單。即使我把頭部處理掉，他也會有其他方法。<br />\n<br />\nRebecca一整個屍體，還在他的手上。<br />\n<br />\n我回到客廳，坐在沙發上沉思。<br />\n<br />\n想著&hellip;&hellip;想著&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n現在我能夠做的只有兩件事：一是追查Rebecca昨天晚上去過什麼地方，然而我沒有調動cctv的權力，這可以說是最大的障礙了；二是確認Rebecca的屍體從哪裡寄來的&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我馬上翻查禮物箱，果然有寄出地址。<br />\n<br />\n這個地址是&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n這並不是兇手的地址，而是Rebecca家的地址。兇手刻意透露這個消息給我知道：要是犯案地址地Rebecca的家，那這件事就變得更不可能了。正常的思考角度是：如果可以翻查Rebecca大廈的cctv，就可以找出兇手。然而兇手留下了這麼大的「線索」，顯然是想誤導我。<br />\n<br />\n不過，我仍然覺得值得一去。"},{"pid":"e0210eefa50d04c4f8946fd813506f3cd8aeebd8","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:59:54.000Z","msg":"再黎"},{"pid":"dfd86a7a0f55e8db713a30a62f504636a3bb67bf","tid":2339211,"uid":92807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T14:23:03.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"781515429011076b55633b09467ab269b507157d","tid":2339211,"uid":305287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T14:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"ad7b2370dbb26be4cce2347efe28c1c014cd8650","tid":2339211,"uid":157414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T14:52:48.000Z","msg":"pushh<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Merry Christmas<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d545d43b9b5f44d43e908e816f059c2302c7e92","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ad7b2370dbb26be4cce2347efe28c1c014cd8650","tid":2339211,"uid":157414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T14:52:48.000Z","msg":"pushh<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Merry Christmas<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T15:00:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a8d66fcf6a77c4798a1fc0dd00bb406b58ac1c","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T15:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaed57ee07ea1b98f28ad71cd819e9d988dcf6c8","tid":2339211,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:01:13.000Z","msg":"